<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qml-computecommand.xml">ComputeCommand</db:link> is used to issue work for the compute shader. The compute shader is specified in the Material component of the same entity the <db:link xlink:href="qml-computecommand.xml">ComputeCommand</db:link> is added to. The <db:link xlink:href="qml-computecommand.xml#workGroupX-prop">workGroupX</db:link>, <db:link xlink:href="qml-computecommand.xml#workGroupY-prop">workGroupY</db:link> and <db:link xlink:href="qml-computecommand.xml#workGroupZ-prop">workGroupZ</db:link> properties specify the work group sizes for the compute shader invocation. <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-dispatchcompute.xml">DispatchCompute</db:link> node needs to be present in the FrameGraph to actually issue the commands.</db:para>
</db:section>
